Go to
HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\WcmSvc\wifinetworkmanager
and change the DWORD strings
WiFiSenseCredShared
WiFiSenseOpen
both to
0

&

Go to
HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\WcmSvc\wifinetworkmanager\config
and change the DWORD string
AutoConnectAllowedOEM
to
0

&

Go to
HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\WOW6432Node\Microsoft\WcmSvc\wifinetworkmanager\config
and change the DWORD string
AutoConnectAllowedOEM
to
0


Finish. restart required.
